Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:18.24,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAD4E22&}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:41.72,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAD4E22&}总会有你的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:49.08,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAD4E22&}在这美丽的星球中
